SQL Project: Music Store Analysis 🎵
📌 Project Overview

This project focuses on analyzing an online music store database using SQL to uncover valuable business insights. 

🎯 Objectives
The main objectives of this project are to:

Analyze customer purchasing behavior
Identify top-selling tracks, albums, and artists
Understand revenue generation across different countries and cities
Find the best customers based on spending patterns
Discover the most popular music genres
Support business decisions using SQL-based insights

📊 Key Business Questions Solved

Who is the senior most employee based on job title?
Which countries have the most invoices?
What are the top 3 highest invoice values?
Which city has the best customers (highest revenue)?
Who is the best customer based on total spending?
Which music genre is the most popular?
Which artist has earned the most revenue?
Which customers listen to Rock music?
Which country spends the most on music purchases?
Which artist contributes most to sales?
